  DATA ld_length_elem TYPE i.

  FIELD-SYMBOLS <ls_fcat> TYPE LINE OF lvc_t_fcat.

  CLEAR r_components.

  LOOP AT i_fcat ASSIGNING <ls_fcat>.

    le_component-name = <ls_fcat>-fieldname.

